Project Objectives: 
                    - To ease down the process of blood donation and searching by
                    - Creating a  user friendly web portal which
                    - Connect(s) all the stakeholders (donor, hospitals, organisations, needy etc.)
  
Specific Modules to be included within the objective:
                    
                    - Sign up for the stakeholders
                    - Searching for the eligible donors by the needy with various functionalities like searching 
                    area-wise etc
                    - The concept of awarding Donor Points
                    - Message and notification to donors by stakeholders at other side of the table
                    - Smart system
                    - Connecting with social networking websites 
